Hello! Thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Gabriel Edwards. How may I assist you today?

Hi Gabriel! I'm really excited to speak with you today. My name is Denise Peterson. I wanted to ask about managing my subscription.

It's great to meet you, Denise! I'd be happy to help you with your subscription. Could you please provide your subscription ID to get started?

Sure thing, Gabriel. My subscription ID is eight seven six five three two.

Thank you, Denise. And for verification purposes, could you please confirm the last four digits of the payment method associated with the subscription?

Absolutely! The last four digits are one two three four.

Thank you for confirming that information, Denise! Now, how would you like to manage your subscription today?

I'd like to upgrade my subscription to the premium package.

Great choice, Denise! I'll go ahead and upgrade your plan to the premium package now. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

No, that would be all for today. Thanks a lot, Gabriel!

You're welcome, Denise! Thank you for your time and for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a wonderful day!
